subject: Preakness Stakes
Horse Racing
Triple Crown (Horse Racing)
Rachel Alexandra (Race Horse)
Mine That Bird (Race Horse)
lead_paragraph: The owner of Rachel Alexandra, the first filly in 85 years to win the Preakness, said the horse may run in the next Triple Crown stage, but no decision has been made yet.
